AWS MANAGER SYTEM:-    
     aws manager sytem is a managment service.
     that helps administartor securely monitors manage , automate & and operate aws resource & server at scale from a centralized console


USES OF MANGER SYSTEM:- 
   1) run command:- 
             execute command an multiple server remotely

  2) session manger:-
              connnect securely to ec2 instance without ssh or rdp

 3) patch manager:-
              automate operating system patching
              security patches automatics update

4) automation:- 
              automate repetitive operation task

5) parameter store:-
              store configuration data & secrets securely

6) inventory managment:-
              collect & track server configruation information


  
